sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Attacker as Attacker VM
    participant Cache as Shared CPU Cache Lines
    participant Victim as Victim VM (Target)

    Note over Attacker, Victim: Shared Physical CPU Socket (Multi-Tenancy)
    
    loop Prime and Probe Cycle
        Attacker->>Cache: PRIME: Attacker fills cache lines with known data
        Victim->>Cache: CRITICAL ACTION: Victim processes sensitive crypto operations
        Note over Cache: Victim operations displace some of Attacker's cached lines
        Attacker->>Cache: PROBE: Attacker reads back their data and measures time
        Note over Attacker: Cache Miss = Long Delay, Cache Hit = Fast Access
        Attacker->>Attacker: Analyzes timing variations to deduce cryptographic keys
    end
